  {
    question: "Can I use both Duolingo and Love Languages?",
    answer: "Absolutely! Many couples use Duolingo for casual vocabulary building and Love Languages for deeper learning, conversation practice, and cultural understanding. Think of Duolingo as a gym workout and Love Languages as a personal trainer."
